General.Name: Maronan Metals Ltd
General.Description: Maronan Metals Limited engages in the exploration and development of mineral resource properties in Australia. It holds 100% interests in the Maronan lead-silver copper-gold project covering an area of 38.35 square kilometers located in Carpentaria Province of Northwest Queensland. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Cloncurry, Australia. Maronan Metals Limited operates as a subsidiary of Red Metal Limited.
